<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/821685-is-this-same-story-book-that-shari">Is this same story/book that &quot;Shari Cooper/Jean Rodriguez&quot; wrote in the book Remember Me 3: The Last Story?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_821685'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F771711.The_Starlight_Crystal">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/821685-is-this-same-story-book-that-shari">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/821685-is-this-same-story-book-that-shari">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/11704968-isabelle"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1344520349i/11704968._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/11704968-isabelle">Isabelle</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
That story was the seed that grew into this one. Many elements are the same, but this book has been expanded into a very different story altogether.
</span>
</div>
