<span id="freeTextContainer14953078320412688474">Teen Creeps made me read this! I missed reading this when I was a kid but I know I would have LOVED it. As an adult, it feels a little rushed, especially the romance (it is short AF after all), but I have to give Pike tons of credit for taking on such an ambitious idea and getting it done in like 200 pages. If this was written in 2018 it&apos;d probably be a trilogy with 1000000000000% more internal monologue and hand wringing, so I&apos;ll take the short version any day.</span>
